    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is best suited for someone looking for a major project or a parts car. The engine currently has significant oil leaks and a noticeable knock, and the transmission slips when shifting into higher gears. Externally, there is visible rust on the rocker panels and several large dents, while the interior shows heavy wear, including torn upholstery and non-functional electronics. It will likely require a tow and extensive mechanical work to be roadworthy again.",
      "price": 6500.0,
